<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Our Project</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        main {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        /* Sections */
        section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        section h2 {
            color: #2762a0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        section ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        section ul li strong {
            color: #0b71de;
        }

        /* Button */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #2762a0;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0b71de;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            main {
                padding: 10px;
            }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }

            section h2 {
                font-size: 1.2em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>PlacoHR</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="about">
            <h2>About Our Project</h2>
            <p>
                The PlacoHR is designed to help students excel in their placement journey by providing a comprehensive platform that focuses on aptitude, technical, and HR interview preparation.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="details">
            <h2>What We Offer</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Aptitude Round:</strong> Practice and improve problem-solving skills with tailored aptitude questions.</li>
                <li><strong>Technical Round:</strong> Strengthen technical knowledge with industry-relevant questions.</li>
                <li><strong>HR Interview Round:</strong> Experience an interactive session with our HR bot, which simulates real interview scenarios and provides insightful feedback.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="goal">
            <h2>Our Goal</h2>
            <p>
                To empower students with the tools and resources they need to confidently face placement challenges. We aim to bridge the gap between preparation and success by creating an engaging, user-friendly platform.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 PlacoHR. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
